description.en: This REC module covers device types (sensors and actuators), device configuration, device actuation, etc.

comments.en: The actuation model is deployed and works in practice with the stakeholders, but we need to update the model to reflect current practice in their systems; e.g., extend the semantics a little and formalize standard state messages, response codes, etc.
